{"id": "software-development--meshcore-watch-app-proof-of-concept", "title": "MeshCore Watch App proof-of-concept", "forum": "software-development", "messages": [{"id": "1459157959560134667", "author": "ferdia", "author_handle": "chocol4t3", "user_id": "185102796591202305", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/185102796591202305/e3542d77f7f6d458e41bf5456f99bf56.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, January 9, 2026 7:12 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-09 7:12 a.m.", "text": "I really wanted to be able to hike without bringing my phone, but still send/receive texts via my apple watch, so I made this proof-of-concept, forked from @ronan 's Swift app. https://github.com/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch Had issues getting the watch to present the 6-digit pin pairing dialogue so I had to disable MITM BLE security in the firmware, and also notifications aren't delivered if the app is in the background, but hopefully both are fixable:)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I really wanted to be able to hike without bringing my phone, but still send/receive texts via my apple watch, so I made this proof-of-concept, forked from <span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"r_o_n_a_n\">@ronan</span>&#39;s Swift app. \n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch\">https://github.com/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch</a>\n\nHad issues getting the watch to present the 6-digit pin pairing dialogue so I had to disable MITM BLE security in the firmware, and also notifications aren&#39;t delivered if the app is in the background, but hopefully both are fixable:)</span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=chatlog__embed-color-pill style=background-color:rgba(30,35,39,255)></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=https://github.com/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">GitHub - fmckeogh/meshcore-watch: MeshCore standalone Apple Watch app</div></a></div><div class=chatlog__embed-description><div class=\"chatlog__markdown chatlog__markdown-preserve\">MeshCore standalone Apple Watch app. Contribute to fmckeogh/meshcore-watch development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div><div class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-container><a class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail-link href=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/ihuPH3kFTYOIVam-0vHQ9vlZd3_k3oJphsHd--pQ2XE/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/7b54c3699684c53b264a3807a1784468f1dbb35aaba1816e5fa356dbfa7b9c4b/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch> <img class=chatlog__embed-thumbnail src=https://images-ext-1.discordapp.net/external/ihuPH3kFTYOIVam-0vHQ9vlZd3_k3oJphsHd--pQ2XE/https/opengraph.githubassets.com/7b54c3699684c53b264a3807a1784468f1dbb35aaba1816e5fa356dbfa7b9c4b/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch alt=Thumbnail loading=lazy data-canonical-url=https://opengraph.githubassets.com/7b54c3699684c53b264a3807a1784468f1dbb35aaba1816e5fa356dbfa7b9c4b/fmckeogh/meshcore-watch> </a></div></div></div></div>"], "attachments_html": ["<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1459157959560134667/1459157959866322964/incoming-3D43D7D7-BF8A-43ED-BF22-EC35434766E3.PNG?ex=69ec06ff&amp;is=69eab57f&amp;hm=d84180177a72813b4da525fce3d601d2a35eba983f0a33fd2f29f1d0872fed1f&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1459157959560134667/1459157959866322964/incoming-3D43D7D7-BF8A-43ED-BF22-EC35434766E3.PNG?ex=69ec06ff&amp;is=69eab57f&amp;hm=d84180177a72813b4da525fce3d601d2a35eba983f0a33fd2f29f1d0872fed1f&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: incoming-3D43D7D7-BF8A-43ED-BF22-EC35434766E3.PNG (58.61 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1459157959560134667/1459157960323367104/incoming-EC513A5D-